{"tid":1350972,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【727光復元朗前哨戰】係元朗西鐵站外搞「元朗恐襲」放映會","createTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T18:03:42.000Z","uid":123943,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"592b019a5de640b708139710447990197b4409db","tid":1350972,"uid":123943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"戰略綱領<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 宣傳光復元朗</span></span></span><br />\n係恐襲嘅案發現場，播返所有恐怖分子嘅罪證，說服力同感染力會倍增，藉此宣傳727光復元朗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2) 突顯政權無能、警察失效</span></span><br />\n元朗鄉黑嘅權力，足以構成無政府主義，甚至係戒嚴狀態，突顯政府無能力管治鄉黑，警察也只能係鄉黑嘅扯線公仔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3) 逼鄉黑露出真面目，令727光復元朗名正言順</span></span><br />\n用放映會，逼鄉黑面對自己暴行，甚至引佢地破壞放映會，激發更大民憤，為727光復元朗造勢<br />\n<br />\n各位要謹記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 無一可失<br />\n官鄉警黑 追究到底<br />\n光復元朗 以武制暴<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"83c0123c158a2f841372a9ec73736096fc2500a6","tid":1350972,"uid":144084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"集合義士保護"},{"pid":"20bff23d30f5a661d04febd1c7c5564c9e8ef562","tid":1350972,"uid":123943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 無一可失<br />\n官鄉警黑 追究到底<br />\n光復元朗 以武制暴<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b3ed12a5015e2d9a5175341dfb87a6bceecc2b1c","tid":1350972,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas